  <entry>
    <title>NexT Optimize</title>
    <url>/2020/06/05/next-optimize/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p> Darunten werde ich über die Optimierung von NexT reden</p>
<p> Below I will talk about the optimization of NexT</p>
<p> 下面将讨论关于NexT主题的优化</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<ol>
<li>设置文章末尾”本文结束”标记</li>
</ol>
<p>在路径/themes/next/layout/_macro 中新建 passage-end-tag.swig 文件,并添加以下内容：</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">{% <span class="keyword">if</span> not is_index %}</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;div style=<span class="string">"text-align:center;color: #ccc;font-size:24px;"</span>&gt;-End-&lt;<span class="regexp">/div&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">{% endif %}</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">&lt;/</span>div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<p>接着打开/themes/next/layout/_macro/post.swig文件，在post-footer前添加代码：</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">{% <span class="keyword">if</span> not is_index and theme.passage_end_tag.enabled %}</span><br><span class="line">   &lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">     {% include <span class="string">'passage-end-tag.swig'</span> %}</span><br><span class="line">   &lt;<span class="regexp">/div&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp"> {% endif %}</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<p>然后打开主题配置文件（_config.yml)，在末尾添加：</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 文章末尾添加“本文结束”标记</span><br><span class="line">passage_end_tag:</span><br><span class="line">  enabled: <span class="literal">true</span><span class="string">`</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<ol start="2">
<li>dd</li>
</ol>
